<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>诸葛灯泡 - 透明化AI代理运营</title>
    <style>
        /* 诸葛灯泡品牌风格 - 奶油手绘风 */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', '微软雅黑', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#d4af37 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 30px 30px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 2px dashed #d4af37;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #d4af37;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #fff9e6;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ffeb3b;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 0;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .dashboard {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px dashed #d4af37;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .card h3 {
            color: #d4af37;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
        
        .metric {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .comparison-section {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px dashed #d4af37;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        
        .comparison-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .competitor-card {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        
        .competitor-card.vox {
            border-left: 5px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .competitor-card.zhuge {
            border-left: 5px solid #FFC107;
        }
        
        .pricing-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .pricing-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .pricing-card {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px dashed #d4af37;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 250px;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        
        .pricing-card.starter {
            border-color: #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .pricing-card.pro {
            border-color: #FF9800;
        }
        
        .price {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .social-proof {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px dashed #d4af37;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        
        .proof-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .proof-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .proof-value {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d4af37;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            border: 2px dashed #d4af37;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            background-color: #d4af37;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #c19d2a;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .agent-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .agent-card {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border: 1px dashed #aaa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .signal-flow {
            height: 100px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffeb3b, #ff9800, #4CAF50);
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .signal-dot {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: signalFlow 3s infinite linear;
        }
        
        @keyframes signalFlow {
            0% { left: -5%; }
            100% { left: 105%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>诸葛灯泡</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">透明化AI代理运营平台 - 运行在公众视野中</p>
            <div class="highlight">我们公开运行每一个AI代理，让客户见证智能决策过程</div>
        </header>
        
        <div class="dashboard">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>实时信号流</h3>
                <div class="metric">432</div>
                <p>当前活跃信号</p>
                <div class="signal-flow">
                    <div class="signal-dot"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <h3>在线代理</h3>
                <div class="metric">8</div>
                <p>实时工作代理</p>
                <div class="agent-grid">
                    <div class="agent-card">销售助手</div>
                    <div class="agent-card">客服代理</div>
                    <div class="agent-card">数据分析</div>
                    <div class="agent-card">市场监测</div>
                    <div class="agent-card">内容生成</div>
                    <div class="agent-card">风险评估</div>
                    <div class="agent-card">财务审计</div>
                    <div class="agent-card">项目管理</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <h3>透明度评分</h3>
                <div class="metric">92%</div>
                <p>客户信任指数</p>
                <div style="height: 20px; background-color: #eee; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 15px; overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="height: 100%; width: 92%; background-color: #4CAF50; border-radius: 10px;"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="comparison-section">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #d4af37; margin-bottom: 20px;">市场竞争对比分析</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">为什么「透明化运营」是AI代理的未来趋势</p>
            
            <div class="comparison-grid">
                <div class="competitor-card vox">
                    <h3>✅ VoxYZ 模型</h3>
                    <ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;">
                        <li><strong>定位:</strong> 5 AI Agents. One Company. Running in Public.</li>
                        <li><strong>监控:</strong> 实时Agent状态可视化</li>
                        <li><strong>信号流:</strong> Demand Radar可视化展示</li>
                        <li><strong>定价:</strong> Starter $79 | Pro $199</li>
                        <li><strong>社交证明:</strong> 700+订阅用户</li>
                        <li><strong>营销漏斗:</strong> 完整转化路径</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="competitor-card zhuge">
                    <h3>💡 诸葛灯泡机会点</h3>
                    <ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;">
                        <li><strong>现状:</strong> 432信号 + 8代理，但缺乏价值主张</li>
                        <li><strong>改进:</strong> 强化透明化运营叙事</li>
                        <li><strong>差异化:</strong> 中文AI代理本土化优势</li>
                        <li><strong>定价策略:</strong> 待制定明确分层</li>
                        <li><strong>社会证明:</strong> 展示企业案例与成果</li>
                        <li><strong>转化路径:</strong> 构建试用到付费流程</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pricing-section">
            <h2 style="color: #d4af37; margin-bottom: 20px;">我们的定价策略</h2>
            <p>透明化运营，透明化定价</p>
            
            <div class="pricing-cards">
                <div class="pricing-card starter">
                    <h3>探路者计划</h3>
                    <div class="price">¥599</div>
                    <p>/月</p>
                    <ul style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: left;">
                        <li>✓ 3个AI代理</li>
                        <li>✓ 500信号/日</li>
                        <li>✓ 基础监控面板</li>
                        <li>✓ 透明化报告</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="pricing-card pro">
                    <h3>先锋计划</h3>
                    <div class="price">¥1,999</div>
                    <p>/月</p>
                    <ul style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: left;">
                        <li>✓ 8个AI代理</li>
                        <li>✓ 无限信号处理</li>
                        <li>✓ 高级监控与预警</li>
                        <li>✓ 专属顾问服务</li>
                        <li>✓ API访问权限</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="social-proof">
            <h2 style="color: #d4af37; margin-bottom: 20px;">我们的成就与信任</h2>
            <p>通过透明化运营建立客户信任</p>
            
            <div class="proof-stats">
                <div class="proof-item">
                    <div class="proof-value">432+</div>
                    <p>活跃信号</p>
                </div>
                <div class="proof-item">
                    <div class="proof-value">8</div>
                    <p>在线代理</p>
                </div>
                <div class="proof-item">
                    <div class="proof-value">92%</div>
                    <p>客户满意度</p>
                </div>
                <div class="proof-item">
                    <div class="proof-value">24/7</div>
                    <p>透明化运营</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="cta-section">
            <h2>开始体验透明化AI代理运营</h2>
            <p>加入我们，成为下一个受益于透明化运营的企业</p>
            <button class="cta-button">免费试用7天</button>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem;">无需信用卡 • 立即访问实时监控面板</p>
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p>© 2023 诸葛灯泡 - 透明化AI代理运营平台</p>
            <p>我们相信透明度是建立信任的关键</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 模拟实时数据更新
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            // 模拟信号数变动
            setInterval(() => {
                const metric = document.querySelector('.card:nth-child(1) .metric');
                const currentValue = parseInt(metric.textContent);
                const newValue = currentValue + Math.floor(Math.random() * 5) - 2;
                if(newValue > 400 && newValue < 500) {
                    metric.textContent = newValue;
                }
            }, 3000);
            
            // 模拟透明度评分变动
            setInterval(() => {
                const metric = document.querySelector('.card:nth-child(3) .metric');
                const bar = metric.nextElementSibling.querySelector('div');
                const currentValue = parseInt(metric.textContent);
                const newValue = currentValue + Math.floor(Math.random() * 3) - 1;
                if(newValue >= 90 && newValue <= 98) {
                    metric.textContent = newValue + '%';
                    bar.style.width = newValue + '%';
                }
            }, 5000);
            
            // CTA按钮交互
            document.querySelector('.cta-button').addEventListener('click', function() {
                alert('感谢您的兴趣！我们将立即为您开通7天免费试用账户。');
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>